A glossary helps define important terms used in the project. It ensures everyone understands the same meaning and avoids confusion.
| Term              | Meaning                                       |
| ----------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| Inventory         | Goods or products stored for sale             |
| Demand Prediction | Estimating future stock needs using past data |
| Stock-in          | Adding items to inventory                     |
| Stock-out         | Removing items from inventory                 |
| Admin             | User with full system control                 |
| Dashboard         | Visual display of stock insights              |
| Alert             | Notification for low stock levels             |
| Historical Data   | Past inventory records used for analysis      |
| User              | Person who operates the system                |
